        <abstract> 
<p>CW’s pamphlet [<hi rend="italic">Darwinism</hi> (1871)] nearly ready. Friends have been much struck by it but say several passages rather obscure.</p> 
            <p>Glad CW coming to England. Will be delighted to see him at Down.</p>
        </abstract>
